name: SubnetNetworkAclAssociation
description: Associates a subnet with a network ACL.

properties.name: SubnetId
properties.description: The ID representing the current association between the original network ACL and the subnet.

properties.name: NetworkAclId
properties.description: The ID of the new ACL to associate with the subnet.

attributes.name: AssociationId
attributes.description: Returns the value of this object's SubnetId property.
